{"tid":330355,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個mv/歌背後的故事","createTime":"2017-07-21T06:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T17:59:06.000Z","uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8728605d5fe1d0d89a661d5da7f2104a4de6b4d8","tid":330355,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T06:37:55.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完呢條片再聽翻首I need a doctor同睇埋歌詞 即刻起雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UeDhFX5hdB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUeDhFX5hdB0&d=lYTXLzsLZtpcSBTv5cf0w%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=985a55e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UeDhFX5hdB0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VA770wpLX-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVA770wpLX-Q&d=lYTXLzsLZtpcSBTv5cf0w%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=0569efde\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VA770wpLX-Q</a>"},{"pid":"ceb18256f10950c7a1880bf6645e89418623f94d","tid":330355,"uid":9741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"林俊杰個首 修練愛情<br />\n<br />\n林俊傑在節目上透露，《修煉愛情》這首歌是寫給在空難離世的女性友人，中學時，女方深深喜歡他，天天送早餐到他家門口，但他沒有接受對方的心意，兩人沒有在一起。<br />\n林俊傑憶起當年，他在報紙上看到女生發生空難，報導把女方的遺物刊出來，他在遺物中發現自己的照片，才知道她一直將自己的照片隨身攜帶。林俊傑坦言：「我看到照片的時候，才想起我有把我的照片給過她，沒想到她一直帶在身上。」林俊傑哽咽地說，他無法想像女生每天送早餐到他家的心情是如何，「我卻沒有接受她的感情，想到就會難過。」<br />\n林俊傑說，後來中學畢業典禮時，女生的家屬透過老師，轉交給他一封信，信封打開後就是那張照片，照片上還有刮痕，有油和海的味道，「那個畫面那種感受我永遠不會忘記」。林俊傑透露，他已經很久沒和別人講這個故事，每每唱這首歌時，他都會把情感收起來，「因為我害怕我唱不下去。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/1639833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F1639833&d=lYTXLzsLZtpcSBTv5cf0w%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=7ef27529\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F1639833&h=09d163ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/1639833</a>"},{"pid":"5233256886e8a35c3c5dc93c7315e27627eed28e","tid":330355,"uid":127503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T17:59:06.000Z","msg":"What are words- Chris Medina"}]}